  not vapor. The biggest debts are documentation drift (agent/skill counts, missing commands, two config schemas),\
  team-mode gaps (memory + config sharing), platform portability (Windows-shaped \cf12 \cb3 .mcp.json\cf2 \cb3 ), and a greenfield blind\
  spot. None of these are structural; all are addressable in a few focused PRs.\
